    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/d9c97d3f7943a7f22de77b6648688652.poster.avif?t=1722267754\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/d9c97d3f7943a7f22de77b6648688652.webm?t=1722267754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/d9c97d3f7943a7f22de77b6648688652.mp4?t=1722267754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Pixel Golf Club</strong> 是一款引人入胜的街机像素高尔夫游戏，让玩家沉浸在精心打造的高尔夫世界中。结合怀旧的像素艺术和现代游戏玩法，它提供了令人愉悦的视觉享受和深度沉浸体验。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >像素艺术美学:</h2></strong> 惊人的像素图形使每个高尔夫球场栩栩如生，增强了整体氛围和视觉吸引力。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放松的游戏玩法:</h2></strong> 平滑且令人平静的游戏玩法，伴随着宁静的音景和环境音乐，提供了完美的逃脱。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战性课程:</h2></strong> 独特设计的课程拥有各种障碍和地形，考验你的精准度和时间感。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能发展:</h2></strong> 通过掌握不同的技术和策略来提升你的高尔夫技能。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸体验:</h2></strong> 沉浸在无尽的绿色草地中，发现击中完美一击的乐趣。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/3a100fbc35512a956e6e478da8c26748.poster.avif?t=1722267754\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/3a100fbc35512a956e6e478da8c26748.webm?t=1722267754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032590/extras/3a100fbc35512a956e6e478da8c26748.mp4?t=1722267754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul></li></ul>",
